# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
YATT_CONFIG[
body_argument: content
body_argument_type: html
]


TITLE: body_argument: content, with type html. (entity var only.)
IN:
 <!yatt:args title>
 <h2>&yatt:title;</h2>
 &yatt:content;
PARAM[
- foo
- <div class="bar">baz</div>
]
OUT:
 <h2>foo</h2>
 <div class="bar">baz</div>


TITLE: widgets can have content argument too.
IN:
 <!yatt:args x>
 <yatt:foo>&yatt:x;</yatt:foo>
 
 <!yatt:widget foo>
 <div class="foo">
   &yatt:content;
 </div>
PARAM[
- bar
]
OUT:
 <div class="foo">
   bar
 </div>
 

